# Automatic Page Refresh Extension - Auto Refresh Plus
## Home
### Feature Showcase
* **Time Interval**: Automated web page refreshing with predefined or custom intervals ensures up-to-date info for tracking stocks, news, or sports.
* **Random Interval**: Allows web pages to refresh at unpredictable times within a set range, which is ideal for avoiding detection and keeping data fresh.
* **Hard Refresh**: Reload pages without relying on cached data, ensuring you access the latest content
* **Set refresh Numbers**: Define how many times you want to refresh the specific webpage, empowering you to manage your browsing sessions efficiently.
* **Display Visual Timer**: The visual timer shows the countdown on the webpage during refresh, which is ideal for tracking live events or auctions. Customize its display and enable it per URL.
* **Stop refreshing when interacting**: Automatic refreshes pause when you click or type on a webpage, ensuring uninterrupted interaction with content and preventing refresh interruptions.
* **Countdown mode**: Schedule page refreshes with the countdown timer. Set by hours for short-term needs or by date for long-term plans like product launches or events.
* **Active Tabs List**: An active tabs list provides an overview of tabs set to auto-refresh, showing timers and settings for each. This is ideal for managing multiple data streams efficiently.
* **Auto start URLs list**: Save time and effort by auto-refreshing predefined URLs upon browser startup. Explore the Auto Start URLs list in Auto Refresh Plus for seamless browsing
* **Refresh Predefined URL**: Setting a predefined URL allows you to refresh a specific webpage automatically without opening it, ideal for frequent single-site refreshes and time savings.
* **URL Changes and Redirection Handling**: Automatically follow site changes to new URLs, ensuring uninterrupted refresh tasks and continuous updates, which is crucial for professionals relying on real-time data.
* **Page Monitor**: Stay alert to any webpage changes, making it easy to monitor when specific text appears or vanishes. This ensures you never miss critical updates.
* **Versatile Refresh Types for Page Monitor**: Update specific webpage parts with a full page refresh or XHR Refresh, auto-click elements, and open monitored links in new tabs.
* **Monitor Types**: Monitor specific webpage changes via visual elements or source code. Track layout, image, and text updates or behind-the-scenes HTML, JavaScript, and CSS changes.
* **Default Target Text / Keyword**: Using a keyword template enhances website monitoring with ease. Customize and automate tracking across multiple sites effortlessly. Simplify your workflow today!
* **Continue Refreshing When the Keyword Found/Lost**: Keep refreshing webpages even after specific keywords are detected or lost. Ideal for continuously monitoring breaking news, stock updates, or dynamic content changes.
* **Window Focus**: The window focus feature automatically brings specific tabs into view for immediate attention when key updates occur, ensuring timely reactions to critical changes.
* **Refresh Predefined Text Keywords**: Easily detect specific text changes on web pages. Set predefined keywords for instant alerts during browsing
* **Get Alerted via Push Notification and Email**: Stay updated with instant notifications. Get alerts when changes occur on your monitored web pages, ensuring you never miss important updates
* **Supported Expressions for Page Monitor**: Define complex conditions with supported expressions for precise webpage monitoring. Ideal for tracking dynamic content changes, price updates, and specific text appearances.
* **Execute Custom script**: Execute custom scripts automatically upon page refresh to automate tasks and enhance functionality, perfect for tailored web interactions and dynamic content management.
* **Hotkeys**: Enhance browsing efficiency with hotkeys for quick control. Set shortcuts for starting a time interval, initiating random intervals, activating timer mode, stopping intervals, and silencing notifications.
* **Your Settings in your control**: Save and export customized settings for backup or sharing, and sync them across devices by logging in. Maintain uniform settings and switch between profiles easily.

