## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
* Can I use Auto Refresh Plus extension free version lifetime? 
Absolutely! Auto Refresh Plus offers its free version for a lifetime, ensuring you receive continuous updates at no cost. However, please note that priority support is not included in the free version.
* Is Auto Refresh Plus compatible with all browsers? 
Indeed! Auto Refresh Plus is compatible with all Chromium-based browsers such as Chrome, Opera, Edge, Vivaldi, and Brave. Additionally, it supports Firefox, ensuring seamless functionality across various browsers.
* Is it possible to synchronize settings across multiple devices? 
Absolutely! Auto Refresh Plus offers a built-in sync system. By creating an account on the ARP website, you can effortlessly synchronize settings across multiple devices. If needed, you can disable sync settings or create multiple settings profiles to maintain uniqueness across devices.
* Does Auto Refresh Plus support international languages? 
Absolutely! Auto Refresh Plus supports various international languages, including Deutsch, English, Français, Türkçe, español, italiano, português (Brasil), português (Portugal), русский, ไทย, 中文 (简体), 日本語, 한국어. We're continually adding support